data.description: Come check out this beauty close to downtown Flowery Branch! NO HOA!  4 bedroom 2 bath with a lot of recent updates. The kitchen is large and spacious with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. The sunroom has a natural gas fireplace and lots of casement windows and French doors that overlooks the country backyard setting. Living room has a natural wood burning fireplace with gas starter.  It has a master on main level with 2 separate closets.  The upstairs features 2 bedrooms and huge bonus room that can by used as playroom or bedroom. We have updated the master bathroom with walkin shower and new sinks etc. We just updated upstairs bathroom with new tub, sinks and tile flooring. The garage floor has been painted along with new insulated garage door with windows. We installed new windows throughout the home.   There is a large gravel sitting area with fire pit in the backyard. Also comes with a 12x24 storage building/ shed for storage etc. It has an 2nd driveway for rv parking etc. Also just installed new main electrical panel with surge protector. We just replaced all interior doors and recently updated main exterior doors. New heat and air unit downstairs and upstairs unit is only 6 years old. The water heater has been replaced within last 3 years. The home has new gutters and gutter guards. We have installed ridge vents in roof. The laundry room was updated within last year with all new drywall and new lvp flooring. Lot more work has been done. Come check it out!
